reviews.text: Tasty, cheap, clean, good service. Definitely one of the best value restaurant in the region
The place looks popular with the crowds, so I tried. It's just okay typical hk noodle soup. The triangle fishball tastes good, the rest is ordinary.

super salty ingredients and even serving you without water
Tasty, recommended
